Available only with the Blum Intivo drawer systems. Be aware that the drawers in this cabinet may not match the drawer system chosen as a default in the room. undefined .

notes.content: we recommend you include all appliance specifications when ordering. If specs are not included, the frame will be replaced by a veneer composite panel with square taped edges and cutouts will be done on site by others undefined .

notes.content: it is recommended that you use 3" screws with washers for installation. These screws are to be installed into wall studs (16" center) in order to secure the cabinet undefined .

notes.content: the maximum cutout size for a single large cutout (double oven) is:  undefined E + F + G = 502" high or E + F + *G = 542" high.

notes.content: will automatically be added in cabinets over 39" wide and 12" high. This vertical divider will be set back from the front edge by 1/16". Each adjustable shelf will be separated into two, one on either side of the vertical center divider. In WebQuoin, each pair of shelves will remain as a quantity of one in the cabinet details undefined .
